Read the payments opportunity analysis plan at `.cursor/plans/payments_opportunity_analysis_650b45db.plan.md` — it is the structural template. Your plan should follow the same architecture (parallel research streams → synthesis → section-by-section writing → review) but be tuned to the specific dynamics of [ENGAGEMENT AREA], and expanded to include the two-part structure, target universe, citation standard, and research retention.

